comments: Bol (ORL) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Suggs (ORL) legally contest Vucevic's (CHI) shot attempt in the post.
Wagner (ORL) is already in Green's (CHI) path and he absorbs the contact to his upper body.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is already in Dosunmu's (CHI) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is already in Green's (CHI) path and marginal contact occurs as Carter Jr. releases away from the contact.
Green (CHI) legally contests Suggs' (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Okeke (ORL) and Caruso (CHI) come together at the same spot and the foot to foot contact is incidental.
Suggs (ORL) contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs after DeRozan has released his shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is already in Caruso's (CHI) path and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.

Replay review of the foul called on Wagner (ORL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Wagner veers overtly and abruptly into Caruso's (CHI) path and initiates leg to leg contact that affects Caruso's ability to defend.
Dosunmu (CHI) is moving alongside Suggs' (ORL) path and he cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is already in Caruso's (CHI) path and is firming up over his left leg when contact occurs.
Vucevic (CHI) legally contests Carter Jr.'s (ORL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Dosunmu's (CHI) left hand makes contact with Suggs' (ORL) right arm prior to Dosunmu making any contact with the ball.
Caruso (CHI) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Bol (ORL) attempts to commit a take foul on Dragic (CHI), and the contact is marginal.
Carter Jr. (ORL) extends his forearm into DeRozan's (CHI) upper body, and the contact occurs prior to DeRozan's gather.
Suggs (ORL) cleanly deflects the ball away from DeRozan (CHI).
Suggs (ORL) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Bulls.
Harris (ORL) commits a take foul on Vucevic (CHI).
Dosunmu (CHI) is retreating alongside Suggs' (ORL) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Dosunmu (CHI) legally contests Suggs' (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Harris (ORL) applies a stayed forearm to DeRozan's (CHI) side, and he immediately removes his arm as DeRozan begins his upward shooting motion.
Okeke (ORL) legally contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
